summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department, accepting an easement from James H. Michaels and Kathryn L. Michaels, Husband and Wife for and in consideration of Mutual and Offsetting Benefits, for a hydrant and appurtenances, over a portion of Tract 10, Sea Breeze Tract, according to the plat recorded in Volume 34 of Plats, Page 42, records of King County, Washington.
